DocWhereRule.Name: CorrectPredefinedType
DocWhereRule.Documentation: The inherited attribute _ElementType_ shall be provided, if the _PredefinedType_ is set to USERDEFINED.
DocWhereRule.Expression: ((('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCIMPACTPROTECTIONDEVICETYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND (PredefinedType <> IfcImpactProtectionDeviceTypeEnum.USERDEFINED)) OR (('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCVIBRATIONDAMPERTYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND (PredefinedType <> IfcVibrationDamperTypeEnum.USERDEFINED)) OR (('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCVIBRATIONISOLATORTYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND (PredefinedType <> IfcVibrationIsolatorTypeEnum.USERDEFINED))) OR (((('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCIMPACTPROTECTIONDEVICETYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND (PredefinedType = IfcImpactProtectionDeviceTypeEnum.USERDEFINED)) OR (('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCVIBRATIONDAMPERTYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND (PredefinedType = IfcVibrationDamperTypeEnum.USERDEFINED)) OR ((('IFC4X3_RC3.IFCVIBRATIONISOLATORTYPEENUM' IN TYPEOF(PredefinedType)) AND PredefinedType = IfcVibrationIsolatorTypeEnum.USERDEFINED))) AND EXISTS(SELF\IfcObject.ObjectType))
